<p style="text-align: left;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/49064700_1545795982.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1杀死一枚诡辩者-标语_750-560 副本 4.jpg"/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">叮！收到一条来自《奇葩说》人气辩手、男神教授「熊浩」的语音消息！</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p><a href="https://app80cx1dod4392.h5.xiaoeknow.com/content_page/eyJ0eXBlIjoyLCJyZXNvdXJjZV90eXBlIjoyLCJyZXNvdXJjZV9pZCI6ImFfNWMxODZkYzJiNWQwMl8xRzZ2dnhMRSIsInByb2R1Y3RfaWQiOiJwXzVjMTg2MmZmYjViMjlfT04zSm9zYkQiLCJhcHBfaWQiOiJhcHA4MENYMURvRDQzOTIifQ" target="_self" style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">点击收听：为什么中国人需要学点逻辑？</span></a></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">&gt;&gt; 逻辑是什么？</span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">一种批判性思维方式，对“是什么”与“为什么”的追本溯源。</span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">即便你想说逻辑没用，也不得不用逻辑的方式表达出来。&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><br/></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0,